uding Leibniz, Kant, Husserl, and Heidegger.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Sep 2020) 0aMelancholy (Philosophy). 0aPhilosophy, Germany20th century. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311070420440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080478664540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804786645423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804786645.jpg  a978-3-11-070420-4  SUP Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles